# Microsoft Azure App Registration Configuration
# Create an app registration in Azure Portal and get these values
VITE_AZURE_CLIENT_ID=your-azure-client-id-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://portal.azure.com
# 2. Navigate to Azure Active Directory > App registrations
# 3. Click "New registration"
# 4. Name: "Teams Message Scanner"
# 5. Supported account types: "Accounts in any organizational directory and personal Microsoft accounts"
# 6. Redirect URI: Web - http://localhost:5173 (for development)
# 7. After creation, copy the "Application (client) ID" to VITE_AZURE_CLIENT_ID
# 8. Go to "API permissions" and add:
#    - Microsoft Graph > Delegated permissions:
#      - User.Read
#      - Chat.Read
#      - ChatMessage.Read
# 9. Click "Grant admin consent" if you're an admin
# 10. Copy this file to .env and update the values